node.text: #circuitbreaker #birthday 2020: The most amazing dinner made by my spectacular mum. Usually I’m out on my birthday. This is the first year in a long time I’ve celebrated with my Milo! ❤️🐶 #circuitbreakersg #victopus #victopusx35 #milothedog #circuitbreakerbirthday
Happy birthday beautiful! What a wonderful spread! I’m drooling! 😘
